Request BIGG reaction

Source: R/5_BIGG.R
request_bigg_universal_reaction.Rd

Request BIGG reaction

request_bigg_universal_reaction(
  url = "http://bigg.ucsd.edu/api/v2/universal/reactions",
  reaction_id = "ADA",
  return_form = c("list", "data.frame")
)

Arguments

url

url http://bigg.ucsd.edu/api/v2/universal/reactions

reaction_id

reaction_id, for example, ADA

return_form

data.frame or list.

Value

universal metabolite information

Author

Xiaotao Shen shenxt1990@outlook.com

Examples

x <- request_bigg_universal_reaction(reaction_id = "ADA", return_form = "list")
x
